  "h1": "Deaf or Hard of Hearing Services",
  "lede": "JFK offers on-demand video interpreting in American Sign Language (ASL) through Convo Now. This service is free and helps Deaf or hard-of-hearing travelers communicate with Airport Customer Service Specialists (ACES). To use it: Find an ACES wearing a red shirt at a Information Center near Baggage Claim. Scan the QR code they provide to connect with a live ASL interpreter in your browser. Access Convo from your phone or tablet",
